#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:1 of
msgid "Compute the 2-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform"
msgstr "计算二维离散傅里叶变换"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:3 of
msgid ""
"This function computes the *n*-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform "
"over any axes in an *M*-dimensional array by means of the Fast Fourier "
"Transform (FFT).  By default, the transform is computed over the last two"
" axes of the input array, i.e., a 2-dimensional FFT."
msgstr ""
"此函数通过快速傅里叶变换（FFT）计算 *M* 维数组中任意轴上的 *n* 维离散"
"傅里叶变换。默认情况下，变换是在输入数组的最后两个轴上进行的，即二维 FFT"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2 of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:8 of
msgid "Input tensor, can be complex"
msgstr "输入张量，可以是复数"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:10 of
msgid ""
"Shape (length of each transformed axis) of the output (``s[0]`` refers to"
" axis 0, ``s[1]`` to axis 1, etc.). This corresponds to ``n`` for "
"``fft(x, n)``. Along each axis, if the given shape is smaller than that "
"of the input, the input is cropped.  If it is larger, the input is padded"
" with zeros. if `s` is not given, the shape of the input along the axes "
"specified by `axes` is used."
msgstr ""
"输出的形状（每个变换轴的长度）（``s[0]`` 指第 0 轴，``s[1]`` 指第 1 轴，"
"以此类推）。这对应于 ``fft(x, n)`` 中的 ``n``。沿每个轴，如果给定形状小于"
"输入，则裁剪输入；如果较大，则用零填充输入。如果未给出 `s`，则使用由 `"
"axes` 指定的轴上的输入形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:18 of
msgid ""
"Axes over which to compute the FFT.  If not given, the last two axes are "
"used.  A repeated index in `axes` means the transform over that axis is "
"performed multiple times.  A one-element sequence means that a one-"
"dimensional FFT is performed."
msgstr ""
"要计算 FFT 的轴。如果未给出，则使用最后两个轴。`axes` 中重复的索引表示对"
"该轴进行多次变换。单元素序列表示执行一维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:23 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `mt.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `mt.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2 of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:26 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axes"
" indicated by `axes`, or the last two axes if `axes` is not given."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 沿由 `axes` 指定的轴（或在未给出 `axes` 时为最后两个轴）进行"
"变换的被截断或零填充的输入。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2 of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2 of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:30 of
msgid ""
"If `s` and `axes` have different length, or `axes` not given and     "
"``len(s) != 2``."
msgstr "如果 `s` 和 `axes` 长度不同，或者未给出 `axes` 且 ``len(s) != 2``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:31 of
msgid "If an element of `axes` is larger than than the number of axes of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axes` 的某个元素大于 `a` 的轴数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:36 of
msgid ""
"Overall view of discrete Fourier transforms, with definitions and "
"conventions used."
msgstr "离散傅里叶变换的总体视图，包含所用的定义和约定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifft2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:39 of
msgid "The inverse two-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "二维 FFT 的逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:42 of
msgid "The one-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "一维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:45 of
msgid "The *n*-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "*n* 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:47 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftshift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:48 of
msgid ""
"Shifts zero-frequency terms to the center of the array. For two-"
"dimensional input, swaps first and third quadrants, and second and fourth"
" quadrants."
msgstr ""
"将零频项移到数组中心。对于二维输入，交换第一和第三象限，以及第二和第四"
"象限。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:51 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:52 of
msgid "`fft2` is just `fftn` with a different default for `axes`."
msgstr "`fft2` 只是 `fftn` 在 `axes` 默认值上的不同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:54 of
msgid ""
"The output, analogously to `fft`, contains the term for zero frequency in"
" the low-order corner of the transformed axes, the positive frequency "
"terms in the first half of these axes, the term for the Nyquist frequency"
" in the middle of the axes and the negative frequency terms in the second"
" half of the axes, in order of decreasingly negative frequency."
msgstr ""
"输出与 `fft` 类似，在变换轴的低阶角包含零频率项，这些轴的前半部分包含正"
"频率项，轴的中间包含奈奎斯特频率项，轴的后半部分按负频率递减顺序包含负"
"频率项。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft2.fft2:60 of
msgid ""
"See `fftn` for details and a plotting example, and `mt.fft` for "
"definitions and conventions used."
msgstr ""
"有关详细信息和绘图示例，请参见 `fftn`，有关所用定义和约定，请参见 `mt.fft"
"`。"

